  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV48">
<l>kuṉṟiṉiṉṟu vāṉiruntu nīḷkaṭaṟki ṭantumaṇ</l>
<l>ṇoṉṟuceṉṟa toṉṟaiyuṇṭa toṉṟiṭantu paṉṟiyāy</l>
<l>naṉṟuceṉṟa nāḷavaṟṟu ṇalluyirpa ṭaittavark</l>
<l>kaṉṟutēva maittaḷitta vātitēva ṉallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Aren’t you the primary Lord who,</l>
<l>—standing on the hill, sitting on the sky, reclining on the wide ocean,</l>
<l>spreading over the unique world, on[ce] swallowing that, dug [it] out</l>
<l rend="indent">as a boar previously—</l>
<l>created the good living beings during the days that went well</l>
<l>and protected [them] by establishing gods for them?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
